<br>
2 Velium Diamond rings [8mr 8fr 8cr 8pr 8dr]<br>
2 Blue Diamond Electrum earrings [4mr 6fr 6cr 11pr 11dr +15 mana each]<br>
2 Velium Blue Diamond bracers [9mr 9fr 11cr 9pr 9dr +30 mana each]<br>
1 Golden Diamond Mask [3mr 10fr 10cr 5pr 5dr]<br>
1 Platinum Blue Diamond Tiara [8mr 8fr 8cr 8pr 8dr +25 mana]<br>
1 Golden Blue Diamond Pendant [4mr 11fr 11cr 6pr 6dr +20 mana]<br>
<br>
This is all fairly expensive stuff, and since the resist changes, I expect the prices to go through the roof.  And, obviously, there's better gear around if you take the time to look for it.  I like the Crown of the Froglok Kings [+20fr +20cr] for Naggy/Vox Dragon raids, for example, rather than the tiara.<br>
<br>
You can also summon some good resist gear: Elemental Blanket is +15 to mr/cr/fr, Dagger of Symbols is +5 mr/dr/pr and Shard of the Core is +15 pr/cr.<br>
<br>
And you have decent fire/cold resist spells - Elemental Armor adds +30 fr/cr.<br>
<br>
Castersrealm has a good guide:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://eq.crgaming.com/data/resists.asp?Class=Magician&Resist=1">eq.crgaming.com/data/resi...n&Resist=1</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
Nobody does their first couple of planes raids with a full set, especially at 46, unless you have a higher level alt who can fund you.  I think my set cost about 15k, and that was with me supplying some of the blue diamonds to a guild jeweler, and having no failures on combines.<br>
<br>
But, by your low 50's, you should have the basic set and be working on getting gear that raises stats and resists at the same time.<br>
<br>
Good luck!<br>
<br>
--<br>
Eloina Pyromancer<br>
53rd Elementalist<br>
